org.lafayette.server.web.fmt

Class HtmlTable<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.lafayette.server.web.fmt.BaseTable<T>
      • org.lafayette.server.web.fmt.HtmlTable<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of formatted object
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Table<T>

    public class HtmlTable<T>
extends BaseTable<T>
    Formats a collection of data objects into a HTML table. Readable bean properties are used to generate the cells.
    Author:
    Sven Strittmatter
